        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>You are right, <a class="mention" href="https://community.frontity.org/u/clayton.collie">@clayton.collie</a></p>
<p>The build directory is generated from the source code, so it is not necessary to maintain a version of those files. You can add it to the <code>.gitignore</code> file without any problem.</p>
